SESSION.DESCRIPTION:
Successful completion of this session indicates the end of the Enrollment reporting run. There is an email sent upon successful completion.
Pre-session SQL is run that deletes rows from TENRL_MONTH_UTIL, based on the parameter PERIOD_ID. The parameters are built in m_Refresh_Enrl_Parms.
Post-session sets TENRL_RPT_CNTL to enrl_reporting_complete status [status = 6]. The parameter is built in m_Refresh_Enrollment_Parms.
SESSION.NAME: s_m_Refresh_Enrollment_TENRL_MONTH_UTIL

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE VRAP.TENRL_RPT_CNTL SET ENRL_RPT_STAT_CD = $$enrl_reporting_complete_stat WHERE ENRL_RPT_ID = $$ENRL_RPT_ID

ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: COMPLETE: Enrollment reporting is complete for the period: $$cur_PERIOD_ID %d

Please contact GDXITD, if there are any questions/concerns.
